{"questionId": "317e80f9", "correctAnswer": "A", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Solve the system by substitution", "content": "From $5y=x$, substitute into $x+y=18$: $$5y+y=18.$$ So $6y=18$ and $y=3$."}, {"title": "Find the matching ordered pair", "content": "Then $x=5(3)=15$. The answer is <strong>(A) $(15,3)$</strong>."}]}